### stream: SSE connection by clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/stream

### 읽지 않은 알림 실시간 수신
### start a cron job every 30 sec
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/SSE
Cookie: access-token={{accessToken_admin}}

### 알림 읽음 처리
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/b1313ccd-60f2-4ef9-8e25-78516024307b/read
Cookie: access-token={{accessToken_user2}}

#################################### 부가 기능

### 알림 목록 조회: all
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Cookie: access-token={{accessToken_admin}}

### 알림 목록 조회: unread
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread
Cookie: access-token={{accessToken_user1}}

### 알림 읽음 일괄 처리
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read
Cookie: access-token={{accessToken_user1}}

### 알림 보내기
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json

